official_title: A bill to authorize the Secretary of Agriculture to acquire certain lands in the country of San Diego, State of California.

summary.text: Authorizes the Secretary of Agriculture to acquire specified lands in the county of San Diego, California, to be administered as national forest lands. Authorizes appropriations of $2,000,000 to carry out the provisions of this Act.
